info.description:
PyISAPIe is a high-performance (much much faster than FastCGI) ISAPI extension
for interpreting Python scripts
in a Windows web server environment such as IIS or Apache. Includes WSGI support
and Django handler support. Tested and working with Trac 0.10. Also tested and
working with Paste/Pylons.
info.keywords: ISAPI, extension, performance, web, www, dynamic, django, trac, wsgi, paste, paster, pylons, apache, cgi, fastcgi, framework, iis
